cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.MA 

Reasoning: 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper presents a multimodal interface for interaction between humans and autonomous systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper focuses on autonomous vehicles and their control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the system uses AI techniques to support situation awareness. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) may be relevant as the paper discusses the development of the MIRIAM system. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) may also be relevant as the system involves interaction between multiple agents (the user and the autonomous vehicle).
